data.description: Welcome to your Dream Home in the Lovely Sunset Mountain Estates of Franklin, NC! This Stunning 3 bedroom, 3 bath home with bonus rooms is an absolute gem.  Features an Open Floor Plan, Granite Countertops, Beautiful Hardwood Floors, Gas Log FP.  Main level living w 2 bd 2 baths, Primary w/ three closets and private bath. Island/bar and pantry in Kitchen.  Laundry and bonus room for a second den or large home office. Attached double carport. Upstairs you'll find a very spacious bedroom ensuite and a private bath. Downstairs boasts full basement with a few finishing touches, plenty of room for rec room, game room, etc. plus add'l storage room, plumbing for another bath and a single car garage. Wrap around Decks on main and lower levels. Dual Zone Central Heat and Air. Two gas hot water heaters. Sizable rooms plus Abundant storage and closet space for all your needs. Paved roads to the front door. You'll enjoy Great Western Mountain views and a tranquil atmosphere. This is the perfect place to call home. Don't miss your chance to own this incredible property. Contact today for a viewing!  $649,000!
